title: Tokyo Game Show 2006-E3_BluRay
description:
Custom Made DVD!!!!

Tokyo Game Show 2006!!!!

No Labels!!!!

Enjoy!!!!



1st disc is just a bunch of trailers from Nintendo that were shown at Tokyo Game Show 2006 and the 2nd disc has a bunch of trailers from Microsoft from Tokyo Game Show 2006 along with the Media Briefing. This was made back in the day so the quality of the menus are not that great but still viewable
